  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you are hit by a melee or ranged attack, you can spend 1 Superiority Die and your reaction to reduce the damage by twice the result.</p><p> If maneuver was in reaction to melee attack, you make a unarmed or weapon attack against the creature.</p><p> On a hit, the creature must make a Wisdom saving throw against your Genjutsu Save DC, being knocked back 20 feet on a failed save.</p><p> If maneuver was used in reaction to a ranged attack, if the attacker is within 90 feet, they must make a Wisdom saving throw against your Genjutsu Save DC, taking twice the result of your superiority die in psychic damage and being knocked 20 feet closer to you.</p><p></p>",
